---
const stages = [
  { name: "Camera / Gallery", icon: "📱" },
  { name: "Background removal", icon: "✂️" },
  { name: "224 x 224 image", icon: "🖼️" },
  { name: "RGB tensor", icon: "🔢" },
  { name: "TF Lite inference", icon: "🧠" },
  { name: "Diagnosis result", icon: "📈" }
];
---

<section id="pipeline" class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header text-center">
      <h2>Processing <span class="text-gradient">Pipeline</span></h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="pipeline-wrapper glass-panel">
      <div class="pipeline-flow">
        {stages.map((stage, index) => (
          <div class="stage-container">
            <div class="stage-node">
              <div class="stage-icon">{stage.icon}</div>
              <div class="stage-glow"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="stage-label">{stage.name}</div>
            {index < stages.length - 1 && (
              <div class="connector-line">
                <div class="moving-dot"></div>
              </div>
            )}
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
      
      <div class="technical-notes">
        <div class="note-icon">💡</div>
        <div class="note-content">
          <p>The model receives a 224 x 224 RGB image. Pixel values are passed in the 0-255 range because preprocessing is included inside the model.</p>
          <p>Transparent background pixels are treated as black during tensor conversion.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .section-header {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
  }

  .pipeline-wrapper {
    padding: var(--space-2xl);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .pipeline-flow {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-m);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
    position: relative;
  }

  @media (min-width: 992px) {
    .pipeline-flow {
      flex-direction: row;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 0;
    }
  }

  .stage-container {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 120px;
  }

  .stage-node {
    position: relative;
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    background: var(--color-bg-base);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-brand-primary);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-m);
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .stage-icon {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .stage-glow {
    position: absolute;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: var(--color-brand-primary);
    filter: blur(15px);
    opacity: 0.2;
    z-index: 1;
    border-radius: 50%;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
  }

  .stage-node:hover .stage-glow {
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .stage-label {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }

  .connector-line {
    position: absolute;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .moving-dot {
    position: absolute;
    background: var(--color-brand-primary);
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--color-brand-primary);
  }

  @media (max-width: 991px) {
    .connector-line {
      width: 2px;
      height: 40px;
      bottom: -40px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
    }
    .moving-dot {
      width: 2px;
      height: 10px;
      left: 0;
      top: 0;
      animation: flowVertical 2s infinite linear;
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 992px) {
    .connector-line {
      height: 2px;
      width: calc(100% - 64px);
      top: 32px;
      left: calc(50% + 32px);
    }
    .moving-dot {
      height: 2px;
      width: 15px;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      animation: flowHorizontal 2s infinite linear;
    }
  }

  @keyframes flowHorizontal {
    0% { left: 0; opacity: 0; }
    10% { opacity: 1; }
    90% { opacity: 1; }
    100% { left: 100%; opacity: 0; }
  }

  @keyframes flowVertical {
    0% { top: 0; opacity: 0; }
    10% { opacity: 1; }
    90% { opacity: 1; }
    100% { top: 100%; opacity: 0; }
  }

  .technical-notes {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-m);
    background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2);
    padding: var(--space-l);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .note-icon {
    font-size: var(--font-size-2xl);
  }

  .note-content p {
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-s);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
  }

  .note-content p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
</style>
